People perceive football club ownership as a lucrative business, really? We’ve caught up with Highlands Park chairman Brad Kaftel.  LISTEN IN SETSWANA:   A go nna le
setlhopha sa kgwele ya dinao gona le letseno le le tona? Nyaa, goya
ka modula setulo wa Highlands Park, Brad Kaftel, o a tlhalosang gore ga gona
letseno le kalo mo kgweleng ya dinao jaaka modula setulo. Go ya ka
ena, o tsene mo kgweleng ya dinao goya ka lerato la yona, mme ntse a sa labella
letsena la yona. O bolella
Daily Sun gore o latlhegetswe ka madi a mantsi gona le go Kenya letseno. Kaftel a re
gona le nako nngwe mo a ntseng a ikemiseditse go amogela dikopo tsa madi gotswa
go bago ba neng bana le kgatlhego ya go reka setlhoka sa gagwe. 